{"article_id":"QStSRiGoqdXbMaYh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. senators on Wednesday are set to probe Brett Kavanaugh , President Donald Trump ' s nominee","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to fill a vacancy on the Supreme Court ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"over his views on abortion","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"as his confirmation hearing moves into its second day .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Here is why it matters :","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"U.S. Supreme Court nominee judge Brett Kavanaugh is sworn in during a Senate Judiciary Committee confirmation hearing on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S. , September 4 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"/Joshua Roberts","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Roe v. Wade is a landmark U.S. Supreme Court ruling from 1973","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that found","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"women have a constitutional right","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to obtain abortions .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The ruling meant","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that states could not ban abortions ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"leading to an immediate and sustained backlash from social conservatives","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that continues to this day .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Why is abortion a key issue in the confirmation hearing ?","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"Kavanaugh could potentially be the deciding vote","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"on overturning the 1973 decision .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The court is currently split 4-4 on ideological lines .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"Justice Anthony Kennedy , a conservative","depth":14},{"id":21,"text":"whom Kavanaugh would replace ,","depth":14},{"id":22,"text":"disappointed conservatives","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"by backing abortion rights in two key cases .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Conservatives hope","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Kavanaugh will seal a majority","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that would at least be willing to curb abortion rights","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"if not overturn Roe .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Senators are likely to question Kavanaugh in detail on his willingness","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to question long-standing Supreme Court precedents .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"The justices are generally reluctant to overturn precedent ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"citing a legal doctrine","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"- known as stare decisis -","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"that counsels against it","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"in order to help the court stay evenhanded","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"and appear less politicized .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"But the court does overturn its precedents .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"In June , the conservative majority did so in a major labor case ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"ditching a 1977 ruling","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that non-union members could be required to make payments to unions","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to pay for collective bargaining representation .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"At a 2016 event at the American Enterprise Institute , Kavanaugh said :","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"\" It ' s appropriate that the court overrule precedent in some circumstances. \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"But he expressed frustration about the lack of a neutral formula","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"for determining when a case should be nixed .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"\" The hard question is when is it appropriate","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"and when is it not .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"I would love to have a perfect answer to that question , \"","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Kavanaugh was not specifically asked about Roe v. Wade .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"During his decade as a judge , Kavanaugh has not ruled directly on abortion","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"but has signaled sympathy for legal arguments","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"made by anti-abortion advocates .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Last October , he was on a panel of judges","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"that issued an order","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"preventing a 17-year-old illegal immigrant","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"detained in Texas by U.S. authorities","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"from immediately obtaining an abortion .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"That decision was overturned by the full appeals court","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and she had the abortion .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"In a 2017 speech , Kavanaugh praised several opinions","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"written by former Chief Justice William Rehnquist ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"including his dissent in Roe v. Wade .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":69,"right":123,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":66,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":65,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":5,"right":67,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":76,"right":122,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":72,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":8,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":9,"right":70,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":16,"right":121,"relati